				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Game Boy Color has 8x8 pixel (per-tile) palette selection, like the MMC5, Super NES, or GBA. It has eight 4-color background palettes (with distinct color 0 in each) and eight 3-color sprite palettes. The palettes are RGB with 32 levels per channel, but the gamma is kind of screwy.</div>

